snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Official Return of Shadaloo Fighting Pass Trailer
snippet.description:
Street Fighter 6 is the latest in the legendary fighting game franchise developed by Capcom. As M. Bison makes their return to Street Fighter 6, players can earn new rewards with the Return of Shadaloo Fighting Pass for July 2024. Earn new special effects for the New Challenger alongside standard items like avatar gear, titles, music, and Fighter Coins by completing tiers. Street Fighter 6 is available now for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).

#StreetFighter6 #Gaming #Games
